{"tid":1387761,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"快d入黎 搵人搞罷工","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:24:40.000Z","uid":40677,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"74f702fafeb082835461cc1a5773b0bf8262fd7c","tid":1387761,"uid":40677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:59.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">建議張所有罷工時間定係同一日</span></span><br />\n搞左一日之後可以比到一支強心針市民<br />\n知道唔係得佢一個罷<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">有人追究罷工就一齊圍佢</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">開左個靚頭就會好多人罷</span></span><br />\n全民罷工！！！<br />\n下次遊行叫口號 唔該叫罷工"},{"pid":"30acc25cd90bc298bfb4cd1175371c33b416f4b6","tid":1387761,"uid":202889,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:04:27.000Z","msg":"借po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有個心理學家話，我地錯曬喎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1386916\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1386916</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n正如呢篇文所講嘅一樣，我地要做到團結不分化嘅第一步，就係要唔好標籤咗大家。<br />\n只有大家都覺得自己係「香港人」，先會願意接受大家嘅幫助，願意一齊罷工，保衛我地嘅家園。"},{"pid":"e692b848cd9e78e0ad284833f0afb90641ac028b","tid":1387761,"uid":40677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"推下啦"}]}